<div class="container-fluid bg-info footer py-2">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <h1 class="text-white heading h6">About Us</h1>
            <p class="content text-white px-2">
                Purneashop.com is a Shopping Site that focus mainly to the purnea areas. If you are from Purnea, you can
